operations.description:
操作列表，必填

支持普通模式和时间线模式：

普通模式示例：
[
    {"action": "move", "params": {"direction": "forward"}},
    {"action": "jump", "params": {}}
]

时间线模式示例：
[
    {
        "action": "move",
        "params": {"direction": "forward", "duration": 2.0}
    },
    {
        "action": "move",
        "params": {
            "direction": "left",
            "duration": 3.0,
            "overlays": [
                {
                    "action": "dodge",
                    "params": {"direction": "forward"},
                    "at": 1.5
                }
            ]
        }
    }
]
